IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Timothy Michael RAMUNDO and Lisa Mary Ramundo Upon the Petition of Timothy Michael Ramundo, Petitioner-Appellant, And Concerning Lisa Mary Ramundo, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0911 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Former spouses appeal and cross-appeal the district court's reduction of the husband's alimony payments. AFFIRMED ON APPEAL AND CROSS-APPEAL.

AFFIRMED ON APPEAL AND CROSS-APPEAL.
